  "@context": "https://doi.org/10.5063/schema/codemeta-2.0",
  "@type": "SoftwareSourceCode",
  "identifier": "dissmapr",
  "description": "Tools to compute and map biodiversity turnover at the macroscale. Provides functions for generating spatial grids, retrieving environmental data, computing multi-order zeta diversity, fitting I-spline models for generalised dissimilarity, predicting community turnover, and delineating and mapping bioregions and their changes over time.",
  "name": "dissmapr: Workflow for Compositional Dissimilarity and Biodiversity Turnover Analysis",
